Subject: [PATCH 804/827] net: macb: Select PTP_1588_CLOCK in Kconfig

This patch comes from:
  https://github.com/Xilinx/linux-xlnx.git

Select PTP_1588_CLOCK by default to allow compilation of
PTP related funcitons.

Signed-off-by: Harini Katakam <harinik@xilinx.com>
Signed-off-by: Michal Simek <michal.simek@xilinx.com>
(cherry picked from commit 5c6f2d0a95f60ef8ca918159256f1cc05ce37433)
Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/cadence/Kconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/ethernet/cadence/Kconfig b/drivers/net/ethernet/cadence/Kconfig
index 988a4ef3..eb7a178 100644
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/cadence/Kconfig
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/cadence/Kconfig
@@ -24,6 +24,7 @@ config MACB
 	tristate "Cadence MACB/GEM support"
 	depends on HAS_DMA
 	select PHYLIB
+	select PTP_1588_CLOCK
 	---help---
